<placeName>廣</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>韶<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>英</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>雄</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>連</placeName>
<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>賀</placeName>
<measure quantity="6" unit="prefectures">
<num value="6">六</num>州</measure>
<term>都巡檢使</term>
<pc>。</pc>代歸<pc>，</pc>提點京城倉草場<pc>。</pc>先是<pc>，</pc>廥積多患地下濕<pc>，</pc>
